==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: feather-brained
<hw>feath"er-brained</hw></mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Giddy; frivolous; lacking seriousness;
given to frivolity; feather-headed.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> airheaded, dizzy, empty-headed, giddy, lightheaded,
light-headed, silly.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Feathered</ent>⟦br⟧
